  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A blast of cold air erupts from your hands. Each creature in a 60-foot cone must make a Constitution saving throw. A creature takes 8d8 cold damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>\n<p>A creature killed by this spell becomes a frozen statue until it thaws.</p>\n<p><strong>Higher Level.</strong>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 6th level or higher, the damage increases by 1d8 for each slot level above 5th.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>FoundryVTT:&nbsp;</strong>Frozen statue element is not automated.</p>",
